        <object placeholders="1" c4Name="User Assessor/Reviewer" c4Type="LLM Agent/Software System" c4Description="Makes sure that the content that is delivered to the user is fit for their preference.&#xa;&#xa;The end goal is to adjust the approach of the whole system based on past events.&#xa;&#xa;Assesses multiple aspects of the user:&#xa;- Looks at what the user has leaned towards doing, are they trying to be with friends more, does this align with their end goals?&#xa;&#xa;Looks at the overall performance of the user over a period of time:&#xa;- Has the user been achieving their stated goals?&#xa;- Has the user been putting things off, has the user constantly put off a certain topic?&#xa;" label="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;%c4Name%&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;[%c4Type%]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#cccccc&quot;&gt;Click node to see more&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" id="fy7l2bzL2NHr767U9Flw-6">
